# Agent / RAG Rule

Agent rules:

- Agent Tool cannot call Mapper or Repository directly; must call Service.
- Agent execution must write trace (see `docs/skills/project-specific/agent-trace-design.md`).
- Agent loops must have max round limits.
- Model output must be validated before persistence.
- AI-generated resources must have review status.

RAG rules:

- RAG answers must include citation sources.
- Retrieval must enforce permission filtering.
- Context must be trimmed to token budget.
- Citation display follows `docs/skills/project-specific/rag-citation-viewer.md`.

Read `docs/memory/AGENT_RAG_MEMORY.md` before agent/RAG tasks.

See `docs/skills/project-specific/spring-ai-agent-tool.md` for Tool implementation patterns.
